SIMPLE: grasping
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grasping
<hw>Grasp"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Seizing; embracing;
catching.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Avaricious; greedy of gain; covetous; close;
miserly; <as>as, he is a grasping man</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Grasp"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Grasp"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Graspless</ent>⟦br⟧
